title: BOLO: 31300
extract_protocol_ch1: Genomic DNA was extracted from whole blood using Proteinase K and phenol/chloroform with standard protocols.
label_protocol_ch1: 200ng of genomic DNA was amplified in an overnight reaction at 37oC. The amplified DNA was enzymatically fragmented, precipitated with isopropanol, and resuspended in hybridization buffer.
hyb_protocol: Resuspended DNA was loaded onto BeadChips arrays and hybridized overnight at at 48oC.  Single-base extension and allele-specific staining was performed by hand.
scan_protocol: After allele-specific staining BeadChip arrays were coated with XC4/ethanol , dried for 1 hour and scanned on a BeadArray Reader (Illumina).
data_processing: Image data was analyzed using GenomeStudio with GT module (Illumina).

label_protocol_ch1: 200ng of genomic DNA was amplified in an overnight reaction at 37oC. The amplified DNA was enzymatically fragmented, precipitated with isopropanol, and resuspended in hybridization buffer.
hyb_protocol: Resuspended DNA was loaded onto BeadChips arrays and hybridized overnight at at 48oC.  Single-base extension and allele-specific staining was performed by hand.
scan_protocol: After allele-specific staining BeadChip arrays were coated with XC4/ethanol , dried for 1 hour and scanned on a BeadArray Reader (Illumina).
data_processing: Image data was analyzed using GenomeStudio with GT module (Illumina).

hyb_protocol: Resuspended DNA was loaded onto BeadChips arrays and hybridized overnight at at 48oC.  Single-base extension and allele-specific staining was performed by hand.
scan_protocol: After allele-specific staining BeadChip arrays were coated with XC4/ethanol , dried for 1 hour and scanned on a BeadArray Reader (Illumina).
data_processing: Image data was analyzed using GenomeStudio with GT module (Illumina).

hyb_protocol: Resuspended DNA was loaded onto BeadChips arrays and hybridized overnight at at 48oC.  Single-base extension and allele-specific staining was performed by hand.
scan_protocol: After allele-specific staining BeadChip arrays were coated with XC4/ethanol , dried for 1 hour and scanned on a BeadArray Reader (Illumina).
data_processing: Image data was analyzed using GenomeStudio with GT module (Illumina).

scan_protocol: After allele-specific staining BeadChip arrays were coated with XC4/ethanol , dried for 1 hour and scanned on a BeadArray Reader (Illumina).
data_processing: Image data was analyzed using GenomeStudio with GT module (Illumina).
